{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 6: Pipeline using LLM The next step is to implement a system pipeline by using the LLM to generate a literature review segment automatically.",
    "The system takes PDFs of multiple papers as input.",
    "It uses the PYPDF2 library to extract the entire text of each PDF.",
    "Then it creates a new thread with the extracted text as a message and submits the thread to the assistant with the extracted text as a query.",
    "Then the response from the assistant is retrieved and the outputs of each paper are merged for the final literature review segment."
  ]
}